text: Jack Flaherty (born 1995) is an American baseball pitcher for the St. Louis Cardinals. Jack Flaherty may also refer to: * Jack Flaherty (gymnast) (fl. 1948), British Olympic gymnast * Jack Flaherty (politician) (born c. 1931), Canadian politician and former member of the Legislative Assembly of Alberta ==See also== *John Flaherty (disambiguation)
title: Jack Flaherty (disambiguation)
